m.com&amp;_nc_gid=5220v0xGsSJKwfqVuRXfJA&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_AfwWbMft9CTIpeIQCSEnU0jEhHiOWdJE-f7YerWiZrnUJQ&amp;oe=69CB087A" alt="Slide 3 fra @fkatwigs" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656506067_18580728574055762_2905980911923489178_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s480x480_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MDE2Mzk3MjI4MDQzMTA4MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5NTkuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Yme-JI7CticQ7kNvwFOAc3N&amp;_nc_oc=Adp0BJ7Dj6hi6p9AiwhWZbn7LZlVrhuctN8jkDHfbcgwNHLa5132n9eUH2tVgDWe-F0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=5220v0xGsSJKwfqVuRXfJA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzgwPVQ1NJBlW8adxS201LUo3rwEZRo0K-erYHE4yjnuw&amp;oe=69CAEB88" alt="Slide 4 fra @fkatwigs" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (20 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@fkatwigs</strong></p><p>woah my first sold out arena show at msg! thank you so much to all the twiglets who have believed in me and supported me for the past 15 years!<br/>
through all the genres i have explored and body movements i have learnt you have always been there to support me and allowed me to grow in all directions, perfectly twisted and nurtured, i am your bonsai tree. you are my super heroes and we are creating a magical sci-fi together. thank you thank you thank you to all of my creative family who helped create this moment with me, more posts to come expressing my gratitude to you xxx</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWSD4ZcibBr/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
